<p>As a guide, you must have an international Passport or other recognized travel documents which should be valid for at least six (6) months from the date of the departure from the last destination of your itinerary.  The company shall assist you to obtain the necessary visas whenever possible.  Service charges and visa fees levied shall be borne by the passengers.  The visa approval is subject and at the sole discretion of the respective country’s Immigration Department / Home Office and Wox Travel & Tour is not liable for the outcome of the application.</p>
