<p>Although most travel, including travel to international destinations, is completed without incident, travel to certain destinations may involve greater risk than others. Wox Travel & Tour W.L.L. urges passengers to review any travel prohibitions, warnings, announcements and advisories issued by the concerned authorities prior to booking travel to international destinations.</p>
